#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.172"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.172:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.172:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga "
msgstr "18. Intention "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: sāriputta-paṭisambhidāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.172:0.3"
msgid "172. Vibhattisutta "
msgstr "172. Sāriputta’s Attainment of Textual Analysis "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.172:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "an4.172:1.2"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti. "
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.172:1.3"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an4.172:1.4"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca: "
msgstr "Sāriputta said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.172:2.1"
msgid "“Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, atthapaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso byañjanaso. "
msgstr "“Reverends, I realized the textual analysis of the meaning—piece by piece and expression by expression—a fortnight after I ordained. "

msgctxt "an4.172:2.2"
msgid "Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi. "
msgstr "In many ways I explain, teach, assert, establish, clarify, analyze, and reveal it. "

msgctxt "an4.172:2.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena. "
msgstr "Whoever has any doubt or uncertainty, let them ask me, "

msgctxt "an4.172:2.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo. "
msgstr "I will answer. Our teacher is present, he who is so very skilled in our teachings. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.172:3.1"
msgid "Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, dhammapaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso byañjanaso. "
msgstr "I realized the textual analysis of the text—piece by piece and expression by expression—a fortnight after I ordained. … "

msgctxt "an4.172:3.2"
msgid "Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.172:3.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.172:3.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.172:4.1"
msgid "Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, niruttipaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso byañjanaso. "
msgstr "I realized the textual analysis of terminology—piece by piece and expression by expression—a fortnight after I ordained. … "

msgctxt "an4.172:4.2"
msgid "Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.172:4.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.172:4.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.172:5.1"
msgid "Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, paṭibhānapaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso byañjanaso. "
msgstr "I realized the textual analysis of eloquence—piece by piece and expression by expression—a fortnight after I ordained. "

msgctxt "an4.172:5.2"
msgid "Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi. "
msgstr "In many ways I explain, teach, assert, establish, clarify, analyze, and reveal it. "

msgctxt "an4.172:5.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena. "
msgstr "If anyone has any doubt or uncertainty, let them ask me, "

msgctxt "an4.172:5.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo”ti. "
msgstr "I will answer. Our teacher is present, he who is so very skilled in our teachings.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.172:5.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
